                      <div class="img-holder">
                      </div>
                      <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="row">
                          <div class="col-md-8">
                            <h2 class="card-title">React Native Developer</h2>
                            
                            <p class="card-sub mb-2 mt-2">Lagos, Nigeria</p>
                            <p class="card-text">We're looking for developer-entrepreneurs and technical business owners to join the Growth team at Paystack as Technical Product Specialists. Developers are one of the most important groups in Paystack's community of partners, and as the Technical Product Specialist, you'll own our developer relations and give Paystack developers the superpowers they need to build amazing products.</p>
                            <p class="card-subtitle mb-2 mt-2"><span>Amount:</span> ₦100,000 - ₦150,000</p>
                          </div>
                          <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="card-apply">
                                <a href="/post/{{id}}" class="btn btn-more">Read More &rarr;</a>
                                <p class="card-status">Status: ongoing</p>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
